rule_right: hospital(t0) ⋀ hospital(t1) ⋀  t0.Hospital_Owner = 'Government - Hospital District or Authority' ⋀  t1.State = 'TX' ⋀  t0.County_Name = t1.County_Name ⋀  t0.Sample = t1.Sample  ->  t0.City = t1.City
